    "description": "The 3e-523-F2 and 3e-523-3 operate as either a gateway connecting a local area network to wide area network (WAN), an access point within a wireless local area network (WLAN), a client within a WLAN, or a wireless bridging device. 3eTI software provides the following major services in FIPS mode: Wireless 802.11a/b/g Access Point functionality; Wireless 802.11a/b/g Client functionality; Wireless 802.11a/b/g Bridge functionality; Wireless 802.11a/b/g Mesh functionality (auto-forming, self-healing wireless capability); IEEE 802.11i.",
